<IfModule mod_proxy.c>

ProxyRequests Off
ProxyPreserveHost On
<Proxy \*>
    Order deny,allow
    Allow from all
</Proxy>

ProxyPass /fedora/objects http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/objects
ProxyPassReverse /fedora/objects http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/objects
ProxyPass /fedora/images http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/images
ProxyPassReverse /fedora/images http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/images
ProxyPass /fedora/get http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/get
ProxyPassReverse /fedora/get http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/get
ProxyPass /fedora/services http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/services
ProxyPassReverse /fedora/services http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/services
ProxyPass /fedora/describe http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/describe
ProxyPassReverse /fedora/describe http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/describe
ProxyPass /iiv http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/iiv
ProxyPassReverse /iiv http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/iiv
ProxyPass /fedora/risearch http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/risearch
ProxyPassReverse /fedora/risearch http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/fedora/risearch
ProxyPass /adore-djatoka http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/adore-djatoka
ProxyPassReverse /adore-djatoka http://localhost:<%= node['tomcat']['port'] %>/adore-djatoka

</IfModule>
